    <li>Deep Learning Indaba 2026 dataset call continues actively. With Nigeria confirmed as the host country and "Sovereign Intelligence" as the theme, the Indaba arrives in August as the first major African ML research conference after the governance events of Q1/Q2 2026. The dataset call is an act of language AI sovereignty — building the training data that makes African AI models possible without dependence on Global North data infrastructure.</li>
